description: Shauna`s Flabébé is an Orange Flower form Flabébé. It performed with Shauna`s Bulbasaur in the final free performance round of the Hiyoku Tripokalon Rookie Class Tournament which was a stage of originality created by a combination of performance and moves. It helped gain enough points with its performance that Shauna was able to win the tournament.
name: Flabebe (Sana)
